{
  "id": "adv_event_2203_01_03",
  "title": "正反対の二人",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "雫、あなたに足りないものはなんだと思う？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ what do you think you're lacking?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.4595690727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "足りないもの……いっぱいあり過ぎて、困って、ます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I lack…so many things…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6666666667,
      "endTime": 11.3618592898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "身長とか、コミュ力とか\nあと、運動神経もあんまり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like height and communication skills…\nAlso‚ my athletic ability is not that great…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5666666667,
      "endTime": 17.7665303867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そうじゃなくて、もっと根本的なこと\n……それは、自信よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I mean something more fundamental.\n…That would be confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.9666666667,
      "endTime": 24.866666666700002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "……確かに、持ってない、です……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Indeed‚ I don't have it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.1666666667,
      "endTime": 28.2598411719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "サニピであれだけ活躍してるし\nNEXT VENUSグランプリで優勝したのに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you're doing great in Sunny Peace‚ right?\nAnd you won the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix‚ didn't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6,
      "endTime": 34.4867798422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "それは……私じゃなくて、みんなの力だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's… not me‚ it's everyone's effort…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6666666667,
      "endTime": 39.0852608363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "自信を持って。あなたには実力がある\nだから、ソロデビューの話が来たのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Have confidence. You have the ability.\nThat's why there's talk of a solo debut for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3,
      "endTime": 45.4334691619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "それは、たまたま昨日、話がそうなっただけ、です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was just a coincidence in yesterday's conversation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6333333333,
      "endTime": 51.2795919736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "うちはそんなことないと思うけどな～\n雫ちゃんの歌ってる声、好きやし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't think we have that kind of thing.\nI like your singing voice‚ Shizuku-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5666666667,
      "endTime": 57.766666762099995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "サニピのソロパートがちょっと長くなったくらいに\n思えば大丈夫だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just that your solo parts in Sunny Peace got a little longer.\nIf you think like that‚ it'll be fine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9666666667,
      "endTime": 63.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "興味はある、けど……やっぱり無理……\n瑠依さんやみんなみたいに、自信、持てない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm interested‚ but… it's still impossible…\nI can't have confidence like Rui-san and everyone else…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2666666667,
      "endTime": 72.87666666659999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "（雫は、自己肯定感が極端に低い……）\n（ずっと気になってたけど、どうして……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Shizuku has extremely low self-esteem…)\n(I've been wondering why for a long time…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.0666666667,
      "endTime": 80.8433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依さん……私は、どうすれば、いいんでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-san… What should I do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1666666667,
      "endTime": 87.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "練習しかない。練習は裏切らないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's only practice. Practice won't betray you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.3666666667,
      "endTime": 91.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "私が自信を持っているのは、誰よりも努力して\n積み上げてきたという経験があるからよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have confidence because I've worked harder\nand accumulated more experience than anyone else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.6,
      "endTime": 98.39925701429999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "……凄い、気迫",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Impressive determination.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.6,
      "endTime": 100.8132199287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "だから雫、あなたにもソロでトップを獲るつもりで\nレッスンをしてほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why‚ Shizuku‚ I want you to practice\nwith the intention of becoming the top soloist.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0666666667,
      "endTime": 107.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "雫が一番、凄いと思っているアイドルを思い浮かべて\nその人に勝つイメージを描いてみて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Imagine surpassing the idol you think is the greatest\nand winning against them in your mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.5333333333,
      "endTime": 114.11150112150001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "イメージ、イメージ……うっ……\nハードルが高過ぎて、かえって、足がすくみます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Imagine‚ imagine… Uh…\nThe hurdle is too high‚ and it only freezes me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4333333333,
      "endTime": 124.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "まさかの逆効果！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unexpected reverse effect!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.6333333333,
      "endTime": 126.9079591592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "一体、誰を思い浮かべたん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who did you imagine?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1,
      "endTime": 129.56056680679998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? What's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.8,
      "endTime": 134.10000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "それは……内緒です……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That… It's a secret…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.3666666667,
      "endTime": 137.24811784430003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ。とにかく、レッスンを始めましょう\n雫、私と合わせて。サニピの曲でいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Phew. Anyway‚ let's start the lesson.\nShizuku‚ join me. How about a Sunny Peace song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.6333333333,
      "endTime": 145.74619570020002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "その……良かったら、トリエルの曲……\nやってみたい、です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… If possible‚ a TRINITYAiLE song…\nI want… to try it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.9666666667,
      "endTime": 154.2166062037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "私達の曲でいいの？　でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our song? But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.4,
      "endTime": 157.9209069729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい……！　お願い、します……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yes! P-Please…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.1333333333,
      "endTime": 160.974648412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん、すごーい！\nどうして一発で合わせられるの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan‚ amazing!\nHow can you match it perfectly in one go!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.2666666667,
      "endTime": 168.8307692309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ映像、何度も観ているので……\nトリエル、大好きだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've watched the live footage many times…\nI love TRINITYAiLE‚ that's why.",
        "id": ""
      },
