    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-rui027.m4a",
      "text": "あなたの気持ちは分かった\n残念だけど、仕方ないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand your feelings.\nIt's unfortunate‚ but it can't be helped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 374.3,
      "endTime": 379.76666666669996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-rui028.m4a",
      "text": "雫の歌、本当に素敵だと思うから……\n今度は私が雫を応援したかったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I truly think Shizuku's singing is wonderful…\nI wanted to support you this time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 379.9666666667,
      "endTime": 387.7483380999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-rui029.m4a",
      "text": "無理強いしてごめんね\n短かったけど楽しかった――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for being pushy.\nIt was short‚ but fun――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 387.9333333333,
      "endTime": 391.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk028.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あの……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ um…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 391.9666666667,
      "endTime": 393.7366893451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk029.m4a",
      "text": "私、一人で歌うのは、無理、です\nだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Singing alone is impossible for me.\nBut…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 393.9333333333,
      "endTime": 400.43333333329997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk030.m4a",
      "text": "いつも輝いている、瑠依さんに、憧れてもいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've always admired‚ Rui-san‚ who always shines.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 400.6,
      "endTime": 405.4592064857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_03-szk031.m4a",
      "text": "だから……新曲……\n私と一緒に、歌ってくれませんか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… for the new song…\nWill you sing it with me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 405.6666666667,
      "endTime": 412.3643235524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
